Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.69,0:01:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 快起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.52,0:01:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,东北战区里捡到的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.12,0:01:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,名字还没起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.71,0:01:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我就叫她「你」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.46,0:01:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 快打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.12,0:01:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,别这么粗暴 她还是个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.02,0:01:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,吉尔 它不是孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.79,0:02:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,它是武器
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.00,0:02:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,武器？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.27,0:02:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,战斗用的道具 而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.56,0:02:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.25,0:02:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我来收养她
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.27,0:02:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.65,0:02:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你愿意接受真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.40,0:02:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经跟陆军那边打过招呼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.87,0:02:25.37,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\pos(548,500)}莱登莎伏特里希
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.87,0:02:25.37,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\be3\pos(440,744)\fad(0,0)}海军委员会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.64,0:02:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我想见迪特弗里德·布甘比利亚大佐！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.77,0:02:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,都说了 你不能见大佐！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.32,0:02:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我有急事要跟他确认！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.54,0:02:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,真烦人！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.45,0:02:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你们在搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.78,0:02:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,大佐 非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.66,0:02:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那个女的一直吵着要找大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.37,0:02:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你退下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.25,0:02:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,还想要命的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.46,0:02:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你来这里干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.17,0:02:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.63,0:03:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,到底武器还是武器
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.59,0:03:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,大佐！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.78,0:03:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,少佐他 吉尔伯特少佐他…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.48,0:03:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,失踪了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.84,0:03:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.59,0:03:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,原来你不知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.25,0:03:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,吉尔伯特…已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.20,0:03:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,胡说！胡说！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.87,0:03:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,少佐一定没有事的！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.24,0:03:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你这表情是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.66,0:03:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,对他来说 只是个道具的你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.81,0:03:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,没有感情 只是个道具的你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.30,0:03:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会感到悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.07,0:03:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么跟她说了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.07,0:03:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得她现在已经能够接受事实了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.99,0:03:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,白痴！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.26,0:03:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么总是这么盲目乐观
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.85,0:03:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,而且一如既往的不懂女人心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.81,0:03:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,快给我去把那个孩子找回来！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.54,0:03:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.18,0:04:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.01,0:04:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,还有…这个孩子是？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.81,0:04:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,总之先带她去洗个澡 然后给她换身衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.69,0:04:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,请问… 跟夫人怎么说？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.19,0:04:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,夫人现在在莱登的公馆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.79,0:04:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不需要告诉她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.85,0:04:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要收留她一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.45,0:04:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这边请
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.36,0:04:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.69,0:04:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.33,0:04:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 不要啊！ 痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.01,0:04:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.71,0:04:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,少爷 虽然我帮她换好衣服了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.13,0:04:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,但这孩子实在太调皮了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.42,0:05:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不 这样就好 没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.39,0:05:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,先给她吃饭 然后带到客房去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.78,0:05:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.48,0:05:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这样会…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.40,0:05:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这样会感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.33,0:05:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,盖上毯子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.61,0:05:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,明天还会更冷的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.54,0:05:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.75,0:05:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 不能到外面去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.11,0:05:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.61,0:05:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.09,0:05:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这孩子 一直在找少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.96,0:05:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,连饭也不吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.94,0:05:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,还不能带她去前线
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.02,0:05:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那个少女状态太不稳定了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.80,0:06:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么反对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.65,0:06:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这可是上面的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.20,0:06:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你也看到那家伙在训练场上的表现了才对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.20,0:06:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,除了杀人 一点用处都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.91,0:06:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,给我带去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.00,0:06:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.02,0:06:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,别这么生气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.99,0:06:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,像这种没爹没娘的小丫头
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.83,0:06:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,派得上用场就只管用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.23,0:06:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,要是她没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.77,0:06:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,丢在战场上就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.01,0:06:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那孩子还…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.05,0:06:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.05,0:06:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,够了 跟你这种伪君子无话可说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.35,0:06:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这是命令 就说这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.62,0:06:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,盖尔达里克帝国同盟军已经入侵波奇亚查
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.33,0:06:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然我们立刻在波奇亚查首都
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.29,0:06:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,卡普里亚外围的河流建立了防线
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.12,0:06:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但现在陷入持久战
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.71,0:07:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我方军力只有3万
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.67,0:07:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,对方有6万
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.59,0:07:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然我们现在维持住了防线
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.99,0:07:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,但敌军把大炮调到了前线
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.93,0:07:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,在那之后 由于遭到炮击 我方士气低落
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.82,0:07:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,阵线有可能崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.63,0:07:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这里 布甘比利亚少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.63,0:07:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.39,0:07:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我想让你带一个中队 去破坏大炮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.14,0:07:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,保证完成任务
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.86,0:07:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你就留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.95,0:07:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,在我回来之前哪都不要去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.80,0:07:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,明白吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.25,0:07:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,少佐 我们准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.85,0:07:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我这就去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.51,0:07:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,少佐 有哨兵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.75,0:08:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.16,0:08:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.71,0:08:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,敌袭！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.29,0:08:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,敌袭！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.02,0:08:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,快联络指挥部！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.63,0:08:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我部遭莱登莎伏特里希袭击！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.92,0:08:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,快迎战！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.92,0:08:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,队长 敌军接近了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.90,0:08:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,突击！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.86,0:09:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.98,0:09:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.62,0:09:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,少佐他…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.81,0:09:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,少佐他在吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.91,0:09:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,少佐他 在这里的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.44,0:09:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,少爷他…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.11,0:10:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,「吉尔伯特·布甘比利亚」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.72,0:10:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,少佐的名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.74,0:10:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,980)\fs54}Violet
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.74,0:10:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,紫罗兰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.92,0:10:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1060,980)\fs54}Violet
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.92,0:10:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你就叫薇鸥莱特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.07,0:10:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你的未来不是道具
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.19,0:10:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,而是与这个名字相称的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.20,0:10:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,薇… 薇鸥…莱特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.14,0:10:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,原来你会说话的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.65,0:10:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,少…佐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.76,0:10:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,薇鸥莱… 莱特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.71,0:10:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.08,0:10:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你是薇鸥莱特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.97,0:10:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,而我是少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.57,0:10:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.93,0:10:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,少佐 我读完了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.07,0:10:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好 下次教你写字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.17,0:11:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,少佐 这是报告书
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.51,0:11:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.67,0:11:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,写得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.59,0:11:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,正好也能兼作练字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.32,0:11:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,以后每天都要交报告
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.21,0:11:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.64,0:11:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,毎日都要交报告
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.14,0:11:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\move(1040,1060,940,1060,0,3000)\blur6}虽然我们没有找到他本人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.85,0:11:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\move(940,1030,1040,1030,0,3000)\blur6}少爷他…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.36,0:11:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\move(1040,1060,940,1060,0,3000)\blur6}但在瓦砾之下找到了他的名牌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.82,0:11:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\move(940,1030,1040,1030,0,3000)\blur6}九泉之下的吉尔伯特也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.60,0:11:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\move(1040,1060,940,1060,0,3000)\blur6}所以把他算作了失踪…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.56,0:11:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,977)\t(1593,2010,1,\blur12)}吉尔伯特…已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.32,0:11:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,今天是感恩节
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.12,0:11:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,三年来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.63,0:11:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这里一直被盖尔达里克军占领
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.37,0:11:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,如今终于得到了解放
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.33,0:11:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,薇鸥莱特
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.93,0:11:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这都是你的功劳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.54,0:11:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,梅希蒂希这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.83,0:11:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,有着在感恩节这天给想要感谢的人送礼的习俗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.72,0:12:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,薇鸥莱特
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.60,0:12:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你有什么想要的东西吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.73,0:12:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,想要的…东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.75,0:12:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.11,0:12:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,想要什么都可以跟我说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.22,0:12:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.29,0:12:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,只要是少佐的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.08,0:12:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.57,0:12:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是我想感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.20,0:12:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,感谢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.86,0:12:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.95,0:12:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你总是奋勇作战…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.61,0:12:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.67,0:12:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.87,0:12:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.88,0:12:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要的 东西 应该是什么样的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.19,0:12:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.29,0:12:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,像你这么大的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.31,0:12:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,应该想要裙子和首饰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.09,0:12:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.16,0:12:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要裙子和首饰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.17,0:13:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.30,0:13:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这里有少佐的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.68,0:13:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,和少佐的眼睛 是一样的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.57,0:13:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,当我看到它的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.67,0:13:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这种…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.28,0:13:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,该怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.78,0:13:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,意下如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.04,0:13:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这胸针很美丽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.63,0:13:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,美…丽…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.08,0:13:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.13,0:13:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道什么是「美丽」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.00,0:14:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,是和「漂亮」相近的词汇吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.80,0:14:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.31,0:14:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不选你眼睛的颜色吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.35,0:14:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,因为 这就是最「美丽」的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.53,0:14:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,之前我不知道这个词 所以从来没有跟您说过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.78,0:14:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,但自从见到少佐眼睛的那一刻 我就觉得很美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.36,0:14:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.87,0:14:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,把胸针给我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.16,0:14:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.03,0:14:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.81,0:15:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.84,0:15:12.80,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,0)\blur3\pos(553,386)}西部战线
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.84,0:15:12.80,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,0)\blur3\pos(460,660)}欧巴伯格
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.80,0:15:16.35,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\pos(1860,530)}莱登莎伏特里希军
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.80,0:15:16.35,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\pos(1770,784)}前线指挥部
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.38,0:15:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,听说盖尔达里克连西部基地都放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.59,0:15:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,看来不到开春就能回老家了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.60,0:15:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,要大家一起回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.63,0:15:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.13,0:15:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,吉尔伯特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.93,0:15:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.64,0:15:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,霍金斯中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.96,0:15:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,别叫我中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.76,0:15:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.52,0:15:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你的军阶比我高
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.86,0:15:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好久没看到你这冷淡的态度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.76,0:15:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,倒开始觉得有点可爱了 真是神奇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.32,0:15:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你也是一点都没变
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.20,0:15:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,只有军衔变成中佐了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.87,0:15:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我是因为总被安排到那些不战而胜的战事里去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.38,0:16:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你家里可是我军的大金主
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.37,0:16:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,指挥部当然也会照顾你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.70,0:16:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,所以啊 升阶了反而觉得丢脸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.93,0:16:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,别说这个了 你还好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.80,0:16:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好好吃饭了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.25,0:16:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,睡好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.69,0:16:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他只是在开玩笑 不要紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.11,0:16:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然年纪比我大 但他是我士官学校时的同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.57,0:16:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,上次在训练场见过的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.60,0:16:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你还把她带在身边啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.86,0:16:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,就是她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.90,0:16:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,在卡普里亚一战立下腥风血雨的战功的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.88,0:16:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,大家背地里都管她叫少佐的「武器」了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.15,0:16:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,就不能让她做点别的么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.63,0:16:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.30,0:16:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.58,0:16:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,她叫薇鸥莱特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.76,0:16:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我给她取的 因为她没有名字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.68,0:16:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,收复英腾斯的这一仗你也要派她？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.36,0:17:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,只要这一仗打胜了 敌军就全线崩溃了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.23,0:17:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕 这就是我们最后一战了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.28,0:17:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.45,0:17:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.62,0:17:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,战争结束以后打算退伍开个公司
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.54,0:17:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,开公司？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.80,0:17:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,到时候我会聘你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.00,0:17:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不想在你手下干活
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.17,0:17:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就雇薇鸥莱特吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.65,0:17:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.11,0:17:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,或许是个好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.58,0:17:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,集合！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.84,0:17:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.41,0:17:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.21,0:17:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,您已经不需要我了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.92,0:17:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.87,0:18:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,处理我的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.79,0:18:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是转属到霍金斯中佐手下去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.26,0:18:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,少佐不会再给我命令了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.85,0:18:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.94,0:18:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,还有几个小时就要决战了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.44,0:18:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这个事情下次再说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.78,0:18:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我来说明作战方案
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.07,0:18:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,敌军的总司令部就在英腾斯这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.33,0:18:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,其四周都是悬崖峭壁 可谓是天然的要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.41,0:18:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,从正面恐怕难以突破
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.11,0:18:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们先由主力部队进行炮击转移敌军注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.62,0:18:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,利用这个机会我们从下水道攻入英腾斯内部
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.34,0:18:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,冲进大教堂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.59,0:18:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,控制敌军指挥部
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.26,0:18:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我们会发射信号弹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.57,0:18:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,向我军发出全军冲锋的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.85,0:18:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我们的作战方案
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.44,0:18:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,听好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.31,0:18:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.94,0:19:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,还有5分钟炮击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.82,0:19:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好 给我上！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.96,0:19:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,炮击开始
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.05,0:19:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,炮击开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.93,0:19:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,发射！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.30,0:19:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,跟上去！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.78,0:19:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,各班 报告状况
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.24,0:19:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,1班有3个人牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.40,0:19:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,2班几乎毫发无损
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.87,0:19:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,3班和4班有一半都掉队了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.37,0:20:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,状态不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.12,0:20:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好 1班2班死守四周
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.22,0:20:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不要让敌军增援靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.41,0:20:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,3班4班跟上来的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.60,0:20:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我一起去控制大教堂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.23,0:20:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,上！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.99,0:20:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.55,0:20:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,发射！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.94,0:20:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,吉尔伯特 好好干啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.52,0:20:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,发射！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.96,0:20:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,少佐！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.90,0:21:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,向右转
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.43,0:21:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,全军 突击！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.78,0:21:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,少佐…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.24,0:22:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,少佐…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.34,0:22:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,少佐！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.29,0:22:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,少佐！少佐！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.67,0:22:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我…没事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.61,0:22:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,少佐！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.11,0:22:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,别管我 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.26,0:22:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,快逃啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.50,0:22:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我做不到！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.53,0:22:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我要带着少佐一起逃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.16,0:22:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我就在…这里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.92,0:23:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那我不逃了！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.96,0:23:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,如果少佐说要留下来 我就在这里战斗到底
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.08,0:23:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,如果少佐说要逃的话 我就带着少佐一起逃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.60,0:23:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,薇鸥莱特！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.81,0:24:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.94,0:24:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对不会让少佐你死的！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.41,0:24:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.00,0:24:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,够了！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.01,0:24:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,活下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.80,0:24:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,薇鸥莱特
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.35,0:24:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你要…活下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.69,0:24:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,自由地活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.65,0:24:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我真心地…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.98,0:24:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,爱着你
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.77,0:25:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,爱？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.11,0:25:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,请问「爱」是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.25,0:25:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,请问「爱」…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.80,0:25:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.72,0:25:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我…不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.13,0:25:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我完全不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.19,0:25:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,少佐！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.03,0:26:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我就觉得你会来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.57,0:26:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这场战斗…真的很惨烈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.60,0:26:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你们发射信号弹之后 我们全军突击
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.94,0:26:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,自知大势已去的盖尔达里克军
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.66,0:26:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,在撤退之前 炮轰了自己的总司令部
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.48,0:26:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你是在这个台阶下面被发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.71,0:26:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕 是那家伙为了保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.04,0:26:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,在炮击的瞬间把你推下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.86,0:26:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,在住院的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.02,0:26:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不论问谁 都跟我说少佐没事
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.12,0:26:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都说不出口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.61,0:27:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你比起自己 要更担心那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.48,0:27:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.85,0:27:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,薇鸥莱特
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.80,0:27:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,要去…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.72,0:27:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.99,0:27:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,除了少佐身在的地方…我哪里都去不了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.44,0:27:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我们回公司去
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.85,0:27:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你是我们公司的 自动笔记人偶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.69,0:27:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那我也待在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.89,0:27:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,直到你愿意一起回去为止
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.35,0:27:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,因为那家伙…把你托付给了我
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.96,0:27:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,就在决战开始前
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.21,0:27:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那家伙特地来找我说——
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.18,0:27:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}万一我有个三长两短
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.50,0:27:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}薇鸥莱特就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.84,0:28:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}等战争结束后
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.23,0:28:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}请把她送到莱登的艾娲嘉登家
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.18,0:28:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}吉尔伯特
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.82,0:28:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.53,0:28:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.14,0:28:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,从来没有 把你当作是战斗用的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.74,0:28:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,而是把你当作一个女孩子 为你的将来着想
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.36,0:28:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.92,0:28:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思了 强行把你拖上来
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.76,0:28:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.74,0:28:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,应该没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.13,0:29:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,刚出院的那阵子 我还在想到底该怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.57,0:29:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你现在 已经能够好好完成人偶的工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.10,0:29:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的很努力
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.50,0:29:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,哪怕没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.86,0:29:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那家伙的命令 相信你也能够活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.21,0:29:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}少佐不会再给我命令了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.21,0:29:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}不是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.97,0:29:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}这个事情下次再说
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.77,0:29:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,公路被封锁了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.57,0:29:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.58,0:29:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经退…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.81,0:29:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,也罢 稍息
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.58,0:29:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.25,0:29:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.71,0:29:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,克斯科莱尔城遭到了盖尔达里克的反动分子袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.81,0:29:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,确实听说过反动势力日渐抬头…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.63,0:30:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,现在状况如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.95,0:30:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然已经控制了局面
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.64,0:30:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但还不能解除周边的警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.58,0:30:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,换条路走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.93,0:30:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.29,0:30:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,薇鸥莱特回来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.67,0:30:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.01,0:30:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,她还会回来上班的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.53,0:30:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你去看看她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.35,0:30:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你去不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.14,0:30:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你这样的人去正好合适
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.27,0:30:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,「我这样的」是什么样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.28,0:30:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我这边可忙着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.58,0:30:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,本尼迪克特
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.56,0:30:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你能去12区那边找找吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.69,0:31:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我去14区看看
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.57,0:31:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.03,0:31:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,新来的快递员把送不完的信给丢掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.03,0:31:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.11,0:31:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要去找回来
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.23,0:31:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.49,0:31:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我们大致猜得到丢在哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.73,0:31:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,薇鸥莱特 你在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.65,0:31:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我不久留 让我进来坐坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.69,0:31:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,让您操心了…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.37,0:31:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,非常抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.91,0:31:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你身体还好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.70,0:31:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好好吃饭了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.83,0:31:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我给你送的东西 就放这了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.37,0:32:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你明天能出来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.01,0:32:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.18,0:32:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,点名要你的委托也有好多
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.59,0:32:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我就像…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.99,0:32:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.59,0:32:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,霍金斯社长所说的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.02,0:32:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,烧起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.10,0:32:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,因为自己曾经做过的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.77,0:32:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}总有一天 你会明白我所说的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.30,0:32:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}然后你会发觉
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.90,0:32:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}自己满身火烧火燎的伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.31,0:32:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要跟她说这种话啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.50,0:32:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你想想她的遭遇 这不是毫无办法的事情吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.97,0:32:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不管有过什么样的遭遇
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.81,0:32:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不管有着什么样的原委
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.54,0:32:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,自己做过的事情是不可抹消的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.09,0:32:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那就忘了过去 重新开始…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.90,0:32:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,忘记也是不可能的 不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.51,0:32:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,烧起来的 不仅仅是那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.07,0:33:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,包括你我
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.65,0:33:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然表面上伤口似乎已经痊愈
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.39,0:33:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,但伤痕始终留在心间
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.43,0:33:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那你说…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.70,0:33:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,该如何是好呢？那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.89,0:33:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,该怎么做 只有她自己才能决定
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.18,0:33:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,在她正视并接受自己满身疮痍的身体之后
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.08,0:33:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.21,0:33:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那孩子失去了少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.21,0:33:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,失去了她所有的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.79,0:33:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.03,0:33:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,因为她并没有失去
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.93,0:33:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都还在
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.53,0:33:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,嘉德丽雅也没回来…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.23,0:33:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,明天我去看看她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.33,0:33:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得暂时应该让她一个人静一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.45,0:33:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.49,0:33:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}我想理解…「我爱你」
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.91,0:34:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}我是为了理解少佐所说的「我爱你」
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.45,0:34:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}才来当人偶的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.96,0:34:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.65,0:34:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,放着她一个人就好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.80,0:34:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.22,0:34:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这样下去那孩子 会连人偶都不做了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.09,0:34:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我想找人代笔
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.81,0:34:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}少佐…
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.79,0:35:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.23,0:35:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}薇鸥莱特
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.88,0:35:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}少佐 少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.64,0:35:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}您没事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.73,0:35:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}你这身衣服是？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.37,0:35:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}现在我在当自动笔记人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.32,0:35:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}你在？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.48,0:35:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}是的 我的工作是代人写信
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.59,0:35:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}写信？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.76,0:35:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}你那双…荼毒生灵的手
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.86,0:35:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}少佐？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.32,0:35:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}怎能写出连结人心的信来？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.41,0:36:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.79,0:37:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,少佐…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.41,0:37:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.68,0:37:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我该怎么办…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.80,0:37:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,请给我…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.42,0:37:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,请给我…命令
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.66,0:38:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,有你的信
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.74,0:38:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,薇鸥莱特·艾娲嘉登
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.96,0:38:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,写给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.01,0:38:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,埃丽卡和艾丽丝托我送来的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.06,0:38:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 信你签收了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.73,0:38:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这么晚了 还在送信吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.61,0:38:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.90,0:38:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我们找到被丢掉的信了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.99,0:38:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,本尼迪克特呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.08,0:38:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那家伙 崴到脚了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.74,0:38:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,都怪他那双鞋子
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.25,0:38:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 你在搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.92,0:39:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,痛痛痛…好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.27,0:39:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就去克拉夫特大街那边了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.57,0:39:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这条巷子就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.37,0:39:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟每一封信
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.07,0:39:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,都饱蘸着深情
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.05,0:39:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,每一封信都是必须要送到的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.83,0:39:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,收到信了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.46,0:39:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.67,0:39:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是爸爸寄来的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.59,0:39:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,信送完了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.81,0:39:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.69,0:39:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.85,0:39:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 每一封信都送到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.21,0:40:18.77,Typing,,0,0,0,,薇鸥莱特 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.95,0:40:21.56,Typing,,0,0,0,,我们本来想去看你的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.49,0:40:25.41,Typing,,0,0,0,,但和艾丽丝商量了以后 我们决定给你写信
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.70,0:40:30.16,Typing,,0,0,0,,人偶给人偶写信或许很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.17,0:40:33.04,Typing,,0,0,0,,但是我想告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.73,0:40:35.12,Typing,,0,0,0,,我们在担心你
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.76,0:40:37.71,Typing,,0,0,0,,还有 我们都在…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.39,0:40:42.06,Typing,,0,0,0,,等你回来
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.44,0:40:48.17,Typing,,0,0,0,,现在 你大概没有心情回来工作
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.57,0:40:49.66,Typing,,0,0,0,,先好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.36,0:40:54.27,Typing,,0,0,0,,万一有什么事情 请不要客气 尽管找我们
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.95,0:40:58.63,Typing,,0,0,0,,我和艾丽丝都相信你一定会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.81,0:41:09.57,Typing,,0,0,0,,还有 今天有个叫斯宾赛的人来找你代笔
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.10,0:41:14.57,Typing,,0,0,0,,说是想给妹妹写一封致谢和道歉的信
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.29,0:41:18.07,Typing,,0,0,0,,他说一定要你来写
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.65,0:41:22.44,Typing,,0,0,0,,不论如何 非你不可
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.95,0:41:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,请问这样可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.04,0:41:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.37,0:41:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,给妹妹写信 总觉得有点害臊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.37,0:41:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不过多亏了她 我找到了工作
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.05,0:41:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,而且有了重新开启人生的信心
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.93,0:42:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,麻烦你了 特地来一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.07,0:42:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,听说你最近在休息
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.02,0:42:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是同事告诉我的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.57,0:42:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,她们给我写了信
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.27,0:42:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那是 我今生收到的第一封信
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.35,0:42:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我理解了…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.89,0:42:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,能收到别人给自己写的信 是如此的开心
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.32,0:42:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,璐琪莉亚也一定会很高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.99,0:42:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.36,0:43:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,「和这个名字…交相辉映」
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.50,0:43:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,「与这个名字…相称」
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.53,0:44:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,薇鸥莱特？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.87,0:44:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,薇鸥莱特？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.32,0:44:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,正如社长所说的
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.13,0:44:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我满身火烧火燎的伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.80,0:44:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.39,0:44:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以…做自动笔记人偶吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.43,0:44:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,活下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.17,0:44:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以…活下去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.26,0:45:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,自己做过的事情是不可抹消的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.80,0:45:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.45,0:45:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.41,0:45:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你作为自动笔记人偶做过的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.80,0:45:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,也是不可磨灭的
